T*
(AI Quant Investment Engine) Tj
T*
(Low-Level Codebase Guide for Junior Developers) Tj
T*
(Generated on: 2026-02-26 19:43:51) Tj
T*
T*
(1\) What this system is) Tj
T*
(This project is an end-to-end data and ML pipeline for investment signals. It collects raw market data,) Tj
T*
(computes technical indicators,) Tj
T*
(trains Random Forest models, generates 1-year and 5-year investment signals, validates data quality, and) Tj
T*
(distributes output through) Tj
T*
(an email report, a FastAPI endpoint, and a Streamlit dashboard.) Tj
T*
T*
(2\) Runtime architecture) Tj
T*
(Main containers are defined in docker-compose.yml.) Tj
T*
(- postgres: stores all raw, feature, signal, and audit data.) Tj
T*
(- airflow-api-server: runs scheduler + API server in one container.) Tj
T*
(- airflow-dag-processor and airflow-triggerer: handle DAG parsing and trigger mechanics.) Tj
T*
(- streamlit: renders the interactive investment dashboard.) Tj
T*
(- api: exposes REST endpoints for signals.) Tj
T*
(- ollama + ollama-init: local LLM inference support for narrative analysis and chat.) Tj
T*
T*
(Ports in use:) Tj
T*
(- Airflow web/API: 8080) Tj
T*
(- Spark UI \(when active\): 4040) Tj
T*
(- FastAPI: 8000) Tj
T*
(- Streamlit: 8501) Tj
T*
(- Ollama: 11434) Tj
T*
(- Postgres: 5432) Tj
T*
T*
(3\) Repository map and ownership) Tj
T*
(Read these files first in this exact order:) Tj
T*
(- dags/ai_quant_daily_pipeline.py: orchestration logic and dependency graph.) Tj
T*
(- src/ingestion/*.py: raw data ingestion into bronze schema.) Tj
T*
(- src/etl/pyspark_etl.py: feature engineering into silver schema.) Tj
T*
(- src/recommendation/train_model.py: model training and artifact persistence.) Tj
T*
(- src/recommendation/strategy_engine.py: inference and signal table writes to gold schema.) Tj
T*
(- src/recommendation/email_alert.py: final reporting + SMTP dispatch.) Tj
T*
(- src/audit/*.py and database/audit_reconciliation_framework.sql: audit layer.) Tj
T*
(- api/main.py and streamlit_app/app.py: serving layer.) Tj
T*
T*
(4\) Data layers and schema strategy) Tj
T*
(The pipeline uses a medallion pattern:) Tj
T*
(- bronze: raw ingested OHLCV or NAV data.) Tj
T*
(- silver: technical indicators and cleaned feature data.) Tj
T*
(- gold: decision-oriented signal tables.) Tj
T*
(- audit: ETL observability, reconciliation, and quality metrics.) Tj
T*
T*
(Common key columns across layers:) Tj
ET
endstream
