T*
(  - atr_14) Tj
T*
(  - stoch_k, stoch_d) Tj
T*
(  - sma_50, sma_200) Tj
T*
(- Drop rows where sma_50 is null \(warmup period filter\).) Tj
T*
(- Write to silver table with mode=overwrite.) Tj
T*
T*
(Important implication:) Tj
T*
(- overwrite mode recreates the full silver table each run for that asset class.) Tj
T*
T*
(8\) Model training internals \(src/recommendation/train_model.py\)) Tj
T*
(Main function: train_model\(source_table, horizon\).) Tj
T*
T*
(Horizons configured:) Tj
T*
(- 1y: 252 days ahead, positive class if future_close > close * 1.10) Tj
T*
(- 5y: 1260 days ahead, positive class if future_close > close * 1.50) Tj
T*
T*
(Labeling strategy:) Tj
T*
(- SQL CTE computes future_close with LEAD\(close, days_forward\) PARTITION BY symbol ORDER BY) Tj
T*
(  event_time.) Tj
T*
(- Rows with null features or null future_close are excluded.) Tj
T*
T*
(Split strategy:) Tj
T*
(- Chronological 80/20 split \(not random\) to reduce look-ahead bias.) Tj
T*
T*
(Model:) Tj
T*
(- RandomForestClassifier) Tj
T*
(- class_weight='balanced') Tj
T*
(- n_estimators 100 for 1y, 200 for 5y) Tj
T*
(- max_depth 12, random_state 42, n_jobs -1) Tj
T*
T*
(Artifacts:) Tj
T*
(- Saved in /opt/airflow/models/<source_table_name>_rf_<horizon>_model.joblib) Tj
T*
(- If dataset is empty, writes a DummyClassifier fallback.) Tj
T*
T*
(9\) Signal engine internals \(src/recommendation/strategy_engine.py\)) Tj
T*
(Main function: generate_signals\(source_table, dest_table\).) Tj
T*
T*
(Inference flow:) Tj
T*
(- Load latest row per symbol from silver source.) Tj
T*
(- Load both 1y and 5y model artifacts.) Tj
T*
(- Compute probabilities with safe predict logic for single-class models.) Tj
T*
(- Convert probabilities to business labels with threshold tables.) Tj
T*
ET
