(16\) Local run and debugging checklist) Tj
T*
(First boot:) Tj
T*
(1. docker compose up -d --build) Tj
T*
(2. verify Airflow UI on port 8080) Tj
T*
(3. run or trigger ai_quant_daily_pipeline) Tj
T*
T*
(Quick health checks:) Tj
T*
(- airflow tasks test ai_quant_daily_pipeline send_opportunity_email <date>) Tj
T*
(- API root at http://localhost:8000/) Tj
T*
(- Streamlit at http://localhost:8501) Tj
T*
T*
(Useful debug targets:) Tj
T*
(- ingestion failures: network/API throttling, symbol list endpoint changes.) Tj
T*
(- Spark ETL failures: memory pressure, JDBC partition bounds, missing id column.) Tj
T*
(- model failures: insufficient history for horizon labels.) Tj
T*
(- email failures: SMTP auth, invalid recipient format, output file permissions.) Tj
T*
T*
(17\) How to add a new asset class \(practical recipe\)) Tj
T*
(1. Add ingestion function that writes bronze.<new>_price_raw with symbol, event_time, OHLCV.) Tj
T*
(2. Add DAG tasks:) Tj
T*
(   - ingest_<new>) Tj
T*
(   - spark_etl_<new> \(dest silver.<new>_features_daily\)) Tj
T*
(   - train_model_<new>) Tj
T*
(   - generate_signals_<new> \(dest gold.<new>_investment_signals\)) Tj
T*
(   - audit + quality + reconcile tasks) Tj
T*
(3. Add optional tabs in Streamlit and API route support in allowlist.) Tj
T*
(4. Add email tab mapping in send_opportunity_email.) Tj
T*
(5. Validate end-to-end with airflow tasks test per step.) Tj
T*
T*
(18\) Common code-level pitfalls to watch) Tj
T*
(- SQL injection risk: some table names are interpolated via f-strings. Keep table inputs controlled.) Tj
T*
(- Overwrite semantics in ETL can remove table-level extras. Re-apply schema changes if needed.) Tj
T*
(- Encoding issues in source comments indicate mixed editor encodings; standardize to UTF-8.) Tj
T*
(- LLM chat prompt currently allows high-certainty investment advice; review compliance before) Tj
T*
(  production.) Tj
T*
T*
(19\) Suggested learning path for a junior developer) Tj
T*
(Week 1:) Tj
T*
(- Read DAG and trace one asset class through all modules.) Tj
T*
(- Run one task at a time with airflow tasks test.) Tj
T*
ET
endstream
