(20\) Final mental model) Tj
T*
(Think of the system as a pipeline of contracts:) Tj
T*
(- Ingestion guarantees bronze row shape.) Tj
T*
(- ETL guarantees feature completeness and indicator semantics in silver.) Tj
T*
(- Training guarantees model artifacts by horizon.) Tj
T*
(- Signal engine guarantees normalized labels and confidence in gold.) Tj
T*
(- Audit guarantees observability and trust.) Tj
T*
(- API/UI/Email guarantee consumable outputs.) Tj
T*
T*
(If one contract breaks, fix the contract boundary first, not the symptom in downstream code.) Tj
ET
